Package: hardcorevisor
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, qemu-system-x86 (>= 8.0), zfsutils-linux
Recommends: etcd-server, prometheus, grafana
Description: Hybrid virtualization platform with Dual VMM
 HardCoreVisor combines Rust KVM core with Go orchestration.
 Supports QEMU and rust-vmm backends with automatic
 workload-based backend selection. Features include:
 .
  - Dual VMM: QEMU (Windows/GPU) + rust-vmm (Linux microVM)
  - REST API + gRPC control plane
  - Virtio block/net device emulation with io_uring
  - ZFS storage, nftables networking, VFIO passthrough
  - etcd-based HA clustering with leader election
  - Prometheus metrics + Grafana dashboards
